âš™ï¸ Technology Stack
Backend
Flask 2.3.3: Web framework

PennyLane 0.32.0: Quantum machine learning

NumPy: Numerical computing

Pandas: Data manipulation

Scikit-learn: Classical ML algorithms

Matplotlib & Seaborn: For generating data visualizations.

Frontend
HTML5: Modern markup

CSS3: Responsive design

JavaScript: Interactive features

Chart.js: For beautiful data visualizations on the web.

Quantum Computing
Variational Quantum Circuits: The backbone of our quantum models.

Quantum Feature Encoding: The process of translating classical data into a quantum state.

Quantum Neural Networks: The hybrid learning models that perform the analysis.

